summary: I was really happy with the character I created so I wanted to upload her here for others to use. She is for the Ningheim race. This is a RaceMenu Preset so that is also required.
descriptionHtml:
Get the Ningheim race [url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35474/?]here[/url].
Everything required by the Ningheim race mod is required here, especially the Ningheim brow pack [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]from this mod[/url].
Rutah tattoo pack is also required, get it [url=http://http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49979/?]from this link[/url].

If you want her to look just like the pictures you need:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion by HHaley[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?]Seductive Lips HD by [b]EcthelionOtW[/b][/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE by Diethardt[/url]
Her body is CBBE curvy.

The armor she is using is the boots from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64258/?]Rogue Genie by BB Drac[/url] and the rest is [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23790/?]Alyn Shir Armor by BloodFree[/url].

Hope you enjoy!
author: HavenStar
